debconf-translator (0.4.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix gettext/LANG support — centralized locale binding
  * Add Settings view (⚙) in sidebar bottom
  * Move all settings (language, SMTP, display) to Settings view
  * Language-neutral UI (no hardcoded Swedish strings)
  * Sort packages: string count, alphabetical, ascending/descending
  * Bigger translation fields (min 60px, max 300px) with scrollbar
  * Show newlines in source text as ↵
  * Per-entry copy-source button (marks fuzzy)
  * Track submitted packages with ✅ green checkmark
  * Warn on resubmission and fuzzy strings
  * Error popups and success confirmation dialogs
  * Welcome dialog explaining workflow
  * Auto-detect language from LANG environment variable

 -- Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>  Tue, 04 Mar 2026 21:15:00 +0100

